  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_56_1",
    "text": "(3) 陆上疆界：2万多干米：海岸线：1.8万多干米.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13575081357508137,
